videos.description: Reid Travis grabs the offensive rebound after a blocked shot and completes the 3-point play.
videos.headline: Travis' concentration leads to and-1 for Stanford

videos.description: Reid Travis flips a shot over his head and gets the bucket and the foul for Stanford.
videos.headline: Travis takes contact but still finishes circus shot

videos.description: Darius McNeill keeps Cal close in the first half after knocking down his fourth 3-pointer.
videos.headline: McNeill buries fourth 3-pointer for Cal

videos.description: Cal's Darius McNeill knocks down his fifth 3-pointer of the half after a step-back move with a hand in its face.
videos.headline: McNeill buries a heat-check 3-pointer
